      <div class="bar"></div>
      <p class="flex items-center mb-2">

Registered office at: A-50, Mansa Ram Park, Dwarka Mor, New Delhi-110 059, India

      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap mb-2">
